description: Frill Holding AB (publ) is a SE-based company operating in Food Products industry. The company is headquartered in Uppsala, Uppsala. The company went IPO on 2019-03-27. Frill Holding AB (publ) is a Sweden-based company, which creates healthy nutrition alternatives based on scientific evidence. The Company’s frozen platform technology permits the creation of smooth frozen textures. The technology can be applied to a number of food categories.
